{"TopicId":171819,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"[1.4] Eject crew action","CreatedByName":"_stilgar_","CreatedById":147818,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T08:13:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"_stilgar_","CreatedById":147818,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T08:13:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that with awesome personal parachutes we have in 1.4, we also need an eject action on crewed parts, that will EVA all crew from selected part (preferably with parachutes armed)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would make easier evacuating a craft that\u0027s going to crash.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T08:58:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf the ones without \u0027chutes ejected, the consequences could be tragic, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T09:30:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlready exists; I\u0027d wait and see how this gets updated and adapted to the stock mechanics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed3348077528\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/148345-131-eva-parachutes-ejection-seats-with-sound-multiple-parachutes/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:214px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"_stilgar_","CreatedById":147818,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T09:35:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223313293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022171819\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520501424\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269278\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cakepie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, cakepie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlready exists; I\u0027d wait and see how this gets updated and adapted to the stock mechanics\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, it doesn\u0027t. I meant stock, the base game. We have parachutes now, but we have to EVA kerbals one by one. When you are crashing, there may be not enough time to evacuate all of them\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223313281\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022171819\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520499503\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167629\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brikoleur\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n36 minutes ago, Brikoleur said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf the ones without \u0027chutes ejected, the consequences could be tragic, though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, right, I forgot that not everyone gets parachutes...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cakepie","CreatedById":69278,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T09:40:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223313295\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022171819\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520501739\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022147818\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022_stilgar_\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, _stilgar_ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbut we have to EVA kerbals one by one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I remember correctly, that mod already allows mass evacuation -- one click, and all occupants will eject (they still have to take turns to go one by one, but you don\u0027t have to do it manually)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-08T13:23:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223313297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022171819\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221520502037\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002269278\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022cakepie\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, cakepie said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I remember correctly, that mod already allows mass evacuation -- one click, and all occupants will eject (they still have to take turns to go one by one, but you don\u0027t have to do it manually)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit does, but \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/147818-_stilgar_/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022147818\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/147818-_stilgar_/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@_stilgar_\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0is looking for this feature to become stock, not as a mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}